      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。方向用TB（从上到下）可以吗？还有，静止和运动状态之间是双向切换的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "direction",
        "Still",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，TB方向可以。静止和运动互相切换，但Crash只能从运动状态进入，而且Crash之后要流向EdgeNode做边缘处理。另外ActuatorController是起点，先到静止状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
