      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把基础结构搭好了：ActuatorController指向Still，Still和MQTT Broker相连，Still与Moving双向互通，Moving指向Crash，Crash再指向EdgeNode。现在需要加样式区分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
